                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1802</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;During recovery, the master had opened all the logfiles, but when it went to open the destination files, it crashed.  The logfile is missing, the edits did not get applied.&lt;/p&gt;

